query:
-- Ver detalhes dos personais duplicados
SELECT 
  p.id as personal_id,
  u.id as user_id,
  u.email,
  u.name,
  p.subscriptionStatus,
  p.createdAt,
  u.createdAt as user_created
FROM personals p
JOIN users u ON p.userId = u.id
WHERE u.email IN (
  SELECT u2.email 
  FROM personals p2 
  JOIN users u2 ON p2.userId = u2.id 
  WHERE u2.email IS NOT NULL 
  GROUP BY u2.email 
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)
ORDER BY u.email, p.createdAt;
